--> Bluetooth 4.0, Bluetooth Low Energy, Bluetooth Smart
	It was madae for IOT purpose only
	The connection is done on the base of requirement or demand
	Their are only 40 channels in low energy
	Single protocol
	Latency of 3ms
	Only Star topology is supported
	For robustness we use the frequency hopping

--> In architecture
	The GAP - Generic Access Profile and
	GATT - Generic Attribute Profile
	
--> It works on the physical layer with ISM band

--> Physical Channels
	37, 38 and 39 channels are used for advertising
	These channels are designed in such a way that it does not interfere with the WiFi channels.
	
